{"pageid":14758,"pagename":"Legends' Guild","title":"Legends' Guild","displaytitle":"Legends' Guild","revid":14266174,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"kartographer_frames","value":1},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Legends'_Guild.png"},{"name":"description","value":"The Legends' Guild is the second most exclusive of the quest-based guilds in Old School RuneScape (with the Myths' Guild being the first). It is located to the north-east of East Ardougne, east of Hemenster and the south of Seers' Village. To enter the grounds of the Legends' Guild, players must have started the Legends' Quest. However, to enter the actual building, players must have completed the entire quest. Radimus Erkle is the headmaster of the guild, and he is also the start point of the Legends' Quest."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Legends&#39; Guild.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Legends%27_Guild\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Legends&#39; Guild\">rsw:Legends' Guild</a></span><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rsc\" data-text=\"CS\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on Legends&#39; Guild.\" data-site=\"rsc\">The RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://classic.runescape.wiki/w/Legends%27_Guild\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"classicrsw:Legends&#39; Guild\">classicrsw:Legends' Guild</a></span></div>\n<small><div class=\"hatnote\"><i>The wiki defaults to the British convention for <a href=\"/w/RuneScape:Style_guide#Numbers\" title=\"RuneScape:Style guide\">floor numbering</a>: Ground floor, first floor, etc.<span class=\"nomobile\"> This may be changed by clicking the moon icon at the top right of the site.</span></i></div></small>\n<table class=\"rsw-infobox infobox no-parenthesis-style\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-header\">Legends' Guild</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-image infobox-full-width-content\"><a href=\"/w/File:Legends%27_Guild.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Legends&#39; Guild.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Legends%27_Guild.png/300px-Legends%27_Guild.png?cddf6\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"210\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Legends%27_Guild.png/450px-Legends%27_Guild.png?cddf6 1.5x, /images/thumb/Legends%27_Guild.png/600px-Legends%27_Guild.png?cddf6 2x\" data-file-width=\"1274\" data-file-height=\"890\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Released</th><td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/20_August\" title=\"20 August\">20 August</a> <a href=\"/w/2003\" title=\"2003\">2003</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:New_-_Legends_Quest!\" title=\"Update:New - Legends Quest!\">Update</a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a></th><td colspan=\"3\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Location</th><td colspan=\"3\">South of <a href=\"/w/Seers%27_Village\" title=\"Seers&#39; Village\">Seers' Village</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Requirements</th><td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\"><img alt=\"Quest points\" src=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a>  <a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Quest\" title=\"Legends&#39; Quest\">Legends' Quest</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Music</th><td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Trinity\" title=\"Trinity\">Trinity</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Map</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content infobox-image\"><a class=\"mw-kartographer-map mw-kartographer-container center\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 300px;background-image: url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_42_53.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_43_53.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_42_52.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_43_52.png); background-position: -10px -210px, 246px -210px, -10px 46px, 246px 46px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\" data-mw=\"interface\" data-style=\"0\" data-width=\"300\" data-height=\"300\" data-zoom=\"2\" data-lat=\"3366\" data-lon=\"2728\" data-mapid=\"0\" data-plane=\"0\" href=\"/w/Special:Map/0/2/-1/2728/3366\"></a></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"2\">Type</th><td colspan=\"3\">guild</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<table class=\"relative-location\" style=\"float:right; width:200px; clear:right;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" class=\"relative-location-header\"><span class=\"relative-location-txt\">Location on <b><a href=\"/w/World_Map\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"World Map\"><span class=\"relative-location-txt\">World Map</span></a></b></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/w/Sorcerer%27s_Tower\" title=\"Sorcerer&#39;s Tower\">Sorcerer's Tower</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\">&#8593;\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:25%\"><a href=\"/w/Hemenster\" title=\"Hemenster\">Hemenster</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:7.5%\">&#8592;\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%; align-items: center;\"><b>Legends' Guild</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:7.5%\">&#8594;\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%\"><a href=\"/w/Entrana\" title=\"Entrana\">Entrana</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\">&#8595;\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/w/Witchaven\" title=\"Witchaven\">Witchaven</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Legends' Guild</b> is the second most exclusive of the quest-based guilds in <i>Old School RuneScape</i> (with the <a href=\"/w/Myths%27_Guild\" title=\"Myths&#39; Guild\">Myths' Guild</a> being the first). It is located to the north-east of <a href=\"/w/East_Ardougne\" title=\"East Ardougne\">East Ardougne</a>, east of <a href=\"/w/Hemenster\" title=\"Hemenster\">Hemenster</a> and the south of <a href=\"/w/Seers%27_Village\" title=\"Seers&#39; Village\">Seers' Village</a>. To enter the grounds of the Legends' Guild, players must have started the <a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Quest\" title=\"Legends&#39; Quest\">Legends' Quest</a>. However, to enter the actual building, players must have completed the entire quest. <a href=\"/w/Radimus_Erkle\" title=\"Radimus Erkle\">Radimus Erkle</a> is the headmaster of the guild, and he is also the start point of the Legends' Quest.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Transportation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Transportation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Guild\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Guild</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Entrance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Entrance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Outside\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Outside</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Ground_floor\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ground floor</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Dungeon\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Dungeon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#First_floor\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">First floor</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Second_floor\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Second floor</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Changes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Changes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Transportation\">Transportation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Transportation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Transportation\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>There are several ways to get to the Legends' Guild:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Quest_point_cape\" title=\"Quest point cape\">Quest point cape</a> teleport - by the entrance</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Fairy_ring\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fairy ring\">Fairy ring</a> code <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>B</b><b>L</b><b>R</b></span> - just east of the entrance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Wizards%27_Guild\" title=\"Wizards&#39; Guild\">Wizards' Guild</a> <a href=\"/w/Yanille\" title=\"Yanille\">Yanille</a> - <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">2<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">nd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 3 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">3<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">rd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; floor 2 in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span>, western portal to the <a href=\"/w/Sorcerer%27s_Tower\" title=\"Sorcerer&#39;s Tower\">Sorcerer's Tower</a>, which is slightly to the north-west of the guild.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Myths%27_Guild\" title=\"Myths&#39; Guild\">Myths' Guild</a> - <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">2<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">nd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 3 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">3<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">rd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; floor 2 in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span>, eastern red <a href=\"/w/Portal_of_Legends\" title=\"Portal of Legends\">portal of legends</a> - front path inside the guild.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Ardougne_teleport\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ardougne teleport\">Ardougne teleport</a> - Go east, then north.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Combat_bracelet\" title=\"Combat bracelet\">Combat bracelet</a> to <a href=\"/w/Ranging_Guild\" title=\"Ranging Guild\">Ranging Guild</a> - Go south-east.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Kandarin_headgear_3\" title=\"Kandarin headgear 3\">Kandarin headgear 3</a>/<a href=\"/w/Kandarin_headgear_4\" title=\"Kandarin headgear 4\">4</a> teleport to <a href=\"/w/Sherlock\" title=\"Sherlock\">Sherlock</a> and run south</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Camelot_Teleport\" title=\"Camelot Teleport\">Camelot Teleport</a> - Go south-southwest</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Guild\">Guild</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Guild\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Guild\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Entrance\">Entrance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Entrance\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Entrance\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:Entrance_of_Legends%27_Guild.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/Entrance_of_Legends%27_Guild.png/300px-Entrance_of_Legends%27_Guild.png?49a41\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"185\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Entrance_of_Legends%27_Guild.png/450px-Entrance_of_Legends%27_Guild.png?49a41 1.5x, /images/thumb/Entrance_of_Legends%27_Guild.png/600px-Entrance_of_Legends%27_Guild.png?49a41 2x\" data-file-width=\"1809\" data-file-height=\"1115\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:Entrance_of_Legends%27_Guild.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Entrance of the Legends' Guild</div></div></div>\n<p>At the gates of the Legend Guild, there are two <a href=\"/w/Legends_guard\" title=\"Legends guard\">Legends guard</a> on duty, only letting players who have started or completed the Legends' Quest go through the gates. If a player who is a member of the guild enters the gates the guards proclaim \"Legends' guild member approaching!\". A player who is currently doing the quest passing through the gates will result in the guards saying \"Hope the quest is going well, [sir/ma'am]!\".\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Outside\">Outside</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Outside\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Outside\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Outside of the actual Legends Guild building is a small house where players can talk to <a href=\"/w/Radimus_Erkle\" title=\"Radimus Erkle\">Radimus Erkle</a> and start the <a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Quest\" title=\"Legends&#39; Quest\">Legends' Quest</a>. Opposite that is a fountain and the <a href=\"/w/Golden_Gnome\" title=\"Golden Gnome\">Golden Gnome</a> statue.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ground_floor\">Ground floor</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Ground floor\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Ground floor\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:Legends%27_Guild_ground_floor.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/Legends%27_Guild_ground_floor.png/300px-Legends%27_Guild_ground_floor.png?27be0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"178\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Legends%27_Guild_ground_floor.png/450px-Legends%27_Guild_ground_floor.png?27be0 1.5x, /images/thumb/Legends%27_Guild_ground_floor.png/600px-Legends%27_Guild_ground_floor.png?27be0 2x\" data-file-width=\"1280\" data-file-height=\"761\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:Legends%27_Guild_ground_floor.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">ground&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 1 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">1<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">st</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; ground floor in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span></div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/w/Radimus_Erkle\" title=\"Radimus Erkle\">Radimus Erkle</a> stands on the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">ground&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 1 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">1<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">st</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; ground floor in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span>. There is also the <a href=\"/w/Totem_Pole_(Legends%27_Guild)\" title=\"Totem Pole (Legends&#39; Guild)\">Totem Pole</a> which was obtained through the completion of the Legends' Quest. The <a href=\"/w/Skills_necklace\" title=\"Skills necklace\">skills necklace</a> and <a href=\"/w/Combat_bracelet\" title=\"Combat bracelet\">combat bracelet</a> can be recharged at the totem. Doing this is a requirement for the <a href=\"/w/Hard_Ardougne_Diary\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hard Ardougne Diary\">Hard Ardougne Diary</a>.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Dungeon\">Dungeon</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Dungeon\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Dungeon\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:266px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:Legends%27_Guild_dungeon_map.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Legends%27_Guild_dungeon_map.png?6f49e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"264\" height=\"274\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-file-width=\"264\" data-file-height=\"274\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\">A map of the dungeon beneath the guild.</div></div></div>\n<p>Downstairs is a dungeon which has <a href=\"/w/Giant_bat\" title=\"Giant bat\">giant bats</a>, <a href=\"/w/Pit_Scorpion\" title=\"Pit Scorpion\">pit scorpions</a>, and <a href=\"/w/Shadow_warrior\" title=\"Shadow warrior\">shadow warriors</a>.\n</p><p>A <a href=\"/w/Dwarf_multicannon\" title=\"Dwarf multicannon\">Dwarf multicannon</a> can be used.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"First_floor\">First floor</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=7&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: First floor\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: First floor\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Going up the stairs from the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">ground&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 1 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">1<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">st</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; ground floor in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span>, on the next floor is <a href=\"/w/Fionella\" title=\"Fionella\">Fionella</a> who runs the <a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild_General_Store\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Legends&#39; Guild General Store\">Legends' Guild General Store</a>. She will buy items from players at a higher price than normal general stores.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Second_floor\">Second floor</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=8&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Second floor\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Second floor\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Players can reach the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">2<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">nd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 3 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">3<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">rd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; floor 2 in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span> via a western and eastern ladder. Up the east ladder is a <a href=\"/w/Bank\" title=\"Bank\">bank</a>. Up the west ladder is <a href=\"/w/Siegfried_Erkle\" title=\"Siegfried Erkle\">Siegfried Erkle</a>, who runs the <a href=\"/w/Legends_Guild_Shop_of_Useful_Items\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Legends Guild Shop of Useful Items\">Legends Guild Shop of Useful Items</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?section=9&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild?action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th>Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/28_April\" title=\"28 April\">28&#160;April</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2016\" title=\"2016\">2016</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Calling_Pets_%26_Deadman_Death\" title=\"Update:Calling Pets &amp; Deadman Death\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>A grammar error has been corrected when entering the Legends' Guild.\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Guilds\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Guilds\" title=\"Template:Guilds\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a c