dimus Erkle\"><img alt=\"Radimus Erkle chathead.png: Chat head image of Radimus Erkle\" src=\"/images/thumb/Radimus_Erkle_chathead.png/17px-Radimus_Erkle_chathead.png?06800\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Radimus_Erkle_chathead.png/25px-Radimus_Erkle_chathead.png?06800 1.5x, /images/thumb/Radimus_Erkle_chathead.png/33px-Radimus_Erkle_chathead.png?06800 2x\" data-file-width=\"62\" data-file-height=\"129\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Radimus_Erkle\" title=\"Radimus Erkle\">Radimus Erkle</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Siegfried_Erkle\" title=\"Siegfried Erkle\"><img alt=\"Siegfried Erkle chathead.png: Chat head image of Siegfried Erkle\" src=\"/images/thumb/Siegfried_Erkle_chathead.png/17px-Siegfried_Erkle_chathead.png?c6434\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Siegfried_Erkle_chathead.png/25px-Siegfried_Erkle_chathead.png?c6434 1.5x, /images/thumb/Siegfried_Erkle_chathead.png/33px-Siegfried_Erkle_chathead.png?c6434 2x\" data-file-width=\"62\" data-file-height=\"129\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Siegfried_Erkle\" title=\"Siegfried Erkle\">Siegfried Erkle</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Monsters</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Giant_bat\" title=\"Giant bat\">Giant bat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Pit_Scorpion\" title=\"Pit Scorpion\">Pit Scorpion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Shadow_warrior\" title=\"Shadow warrior\">Shadow warrior</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Shops</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Legends_Guild_General_Store.\" title=\"Legends Guild General Store.\">Legends Guild General Store.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Legends_Guild_Shop_of_Useful_Items.\" title=\"Legends Guild Shop of Useful Items.\">Legends Guild Shop of Useful Items.</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Cape_of_legends\" title=\"Cape of legends\"><img alt=\"Cape of legends.png\" src=\"/images/Cape_of_legends.png?3c432\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Cape_of_legends\" title=\"Cape of legends\">Cape of legends</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Dragon_sq_shield\" title=\"Dragon sq shield\"><img alt=\"Dragon sq shield.png\" src=\"/images/Dragon_sq_shield.png?8fa13\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"26\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"26\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Dragon_sq_shield\" title=\"Dragon sq shield\">Dragon sq shield</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Golden_Gnome\" title=\"Golden Gnome\">Golden Gnome</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Quest\" title=\"Legends&#39; Quest\">Legends' Quest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Totem_Pole_(Legends%27_Guild)\" title=\"Totem Pole (Legends&#39; Guild)\">Totem Pole</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐67df7655d‐czd4b\nCached time: 20220420225611\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.136 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.164 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 770/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 33217/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1473/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 778/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.035/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1726977/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   94.384      1 -total\n 29.52%   27.862      1 Template:Infobox_Location\n 19.39%   18.303      3 Template:Navbox\n 16.72%   15.783      1 Template:Guilds\n 14.00%   13.212      1 Template:External\n 13.11%   12.372      6 Template:FloorNumber\n  9.14%    8.622      1 Template:Map\n  8.75%    8.261      1 Template:Legends'_Guild\n  4.79%    4.521      1 Template:Relativelocation\n  4.47%    4.219      2 Template:Ctg\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:14758-0!canonical and timestamp 20220420225611 and revision id 14266174. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{external|rs|rsc}}\n{{Floor}}\n{{Infobox Location\n|name = Legends' Guild\n|image = [[File:Legends' Guild.png|300px]]\n|release = [[20 August]] [[2003]]\n|update = New - Legends Quest!\n|members = Yes\n|location = South of [[Seers' Village]]\n|requirement = {{SCP|Quest}} [[Legends' Quest]]\n|music = [[Trinity]]\n|map = {{Map|name=Legends' Guild|x=2728|y=3366}}\n|type = guild\n}}\n{{Relativelocation\n|location = Legends' Guild\n|north = Sorcerer's Tower\n|west = Hemenster\n|south = Witchaven\n|east = Entrana\n}}\nThe '''Legends' Guild''' is the second most exclusive of the quest-based guilds in ''Old School RuneScape'' (with the [[Myths' Guild]] being the first). It is located to the north-east of [[East Ardougne]], east of [[Hemenster]] and the south of [[Seers' Village]]. To enter the grounds of the Legends' Guild, players must have started the [[Legends' Quest]]. However, to enter the actual building, players must have completed the entire quest. [[Radimus Erkle]] is the headmaster of the guild, and he is also the start point of the Legends' Quest.\n\n==Transportation==\nThere are several ways to get to the Legends' Guild:\n*[[Quest point cape]] teleport - by the entrance\n*[[Fairy ring]] code {{Fairycode|BLR}} - just east of the entrance.\n*[[Wizards' Guild]] [[Yanille]] - {{FloorNumber|uk=2}}, western portal to the [[Sorcerer's Tower]], which is slightly to the north-west of the guild.\n*[[Myths' Guild]] - {{FloorNumber|uk=2}}, eastern red [[Portal of Legends|portal of legends]] - front path inside the guild.\n*[[Ardougne teleport]] - Go east, then north.\n*[[Combat bracelet]] to [[Ranging Guild]] - Go south-east.\n*[[Kandarin headgear 3]]/[[Kandarin headgear_4|4]] teleport to [[Sherlock]] and run south\n*[[Camelot Teleport]] - Go south-southwest\n\n==Guild==\n===Entrance===\n[[File:Entrance of Legends' Guild.png|thumb|Entrance of the Legends' Guild]]\nAt the gates of the Legend Guild, there are two [[Legends guard]] on duty, only letting players who have started or completed the Legends' Quest go through the gates. If a player who is a member of the guild enters the gates the guards proclaim \"Legends' guild member approaching!\". A player who is currently doing the quest passing through the gates will result in the guards saying \"Hope the quest is going well, [sir/ma'am]!\".\n\n===Outside===\nOutside of the actual Legends Guild building is a small house where players can talk to [[Radimus Erkle]] and start the [[Legends' Quest]]. Opposite that is a fountain and the [[Golden Gnome]] statue.\n\n===Ground floor===\n[[File:Legends' Guild ground floor.png|thumb|The {{FloorNumber|uk=0}}]]\n[[Radimus Erkle]] stands on the {{FloorNumber|uk=0}}. There is also the [[Totem Pole (Legends' Guild)|Totem Pole]] which was obtained through the completion of the Legends' Quest. The [[skills necklace]] and [[combat bracelet]] can be recharged at the totem. Doing this is a requirement for the [[Hard Ardougne Diary]].\n\n===Dungeon===\n[[File:Legends' Guild dungeon map.png|frame|left|A map of the dungeon beneath the guild.]]\nDownstairs is a dungeon which has [[giant bat]]s, [[Pit Scorpion|pit scorpion]]s, and [[shadow warrior]]s.\n\nA [[Dwarf multicannon]] can be used.\n\n===First floor===\nGoing up the stairs from the {{FloorNumber|uk=0}}, on the next floor is [[Fionella]] who runs the [[Legends' Guild General Store]]. She will buy items from players at a higher price than normal general stores.\n\n===Second floor===\nPlayers can reach the {{FloorNumber|uk=2}} via a western and eastern ladder. Up the east ladder is a [[bank]]. Up the west ladder is [[Siegfried Erkle]], who runs the [[Legends Guild Shop of Useful Items]].\n\n==Changes==\n{{Subject changes header}}\n{{Subject changes\n|date = 28 April 2016\n|update = Calling Pets & Deadman Death\n|poll = \n|change = A grammar error has been corrected when entering the Legends' Guild.\n}}\n{{Subject changes footer}}\n\n{{Guilds}}\n{{Legends' Guild}}"}